The paper proposes a machine learning algorithm for odor recognition, which involves deep learning and nearest class mean method. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves image processing and feature extraction, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper deals with classification tasks, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves natural language processing, which could also suggest cs.CL (Computation and Language) as a possible sub-category.
